                <mxCell id="mt_explain" value="Both mediators are long-lived threads iterating via tracer.iter[:].  Frame locals (h5, logits_list) persist on each rank across steps.&#10;Each step: rank 0 re-captures h5.  Rank 1 pulls the FRESH value lazily when h5*2 is evaluated.  No thread serialization, no push-all." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontSize=9;align=left;spacingLeft=8;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;" parent="mt_box" vertex="1">
